message.body: Hey, could you let me know when you're free to rehearse any time during the day or at night every day this week? Also dress rehearsal is Thursday night plus like 15 minutes Friday night.
What about the rest of the week?
Would tomorrow between 11 and 12:30 work for you?
Yep. Lets hope I wake up in time I shall try very very hard
Hahaha actually I don't think I need you tomorrow we had to change locations. I'll let you know when I will need you though. Thanks!
